obstacleVisualizer

Class Obstacle

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.shape.Shape3D
        • obstacleVisualizer.Obstacle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class Obstacle
extends javafx.scene.shape.Shape3D
    Class for description 3D obstacle in space. Represents a Shape3D with custom Mesh and Material. Realize methods for to check intersection.
